sub_sections.text:
a supply consisting of the characteristics of a single supply from an
economic point of view shall not be artificially split;
Page 25 10/21/2013

the essential features of a transaction shall be ascertained to
determine whether the supply is single or more than one distinct
supply;

the supply, if constituted with one or more elements, shall be a single
supply, and other elements shall be regarded as part of such a single
supply;
